data.description: This beautiful single-family home has so much to offer! You are welcomed into the living room featuring gorgeous hardwood floors that continue throughout the home! The living room also offers large picture windows allowing for tons of natural light! Continue through to the kitchen featuring tons of counter space and beautiful tiled backsplash! Two of the bedrooms are located on the first floor featuring hardwood floors and large windows that allow light to flood in! The full bathroom on the mail floor features a tiled shower/tub combination! Continue upstairs where you will find an incredibly spacious third bedroom! This room is complete with plush carpeting, vaulted ceilings and plenty of space for storage! Make your way down to the fully finished basement! This basement is perfect for a rec room, playroom or additional living space! There is plenty of storage space and a separate laundry area! Outside you will find a large backyard and an attached 1-car garage! With easy highway access, this is near food, shopping and public transit! This won't last long! Schedule a showing to see it for yourself!
